{
  "texts": [
    "This approach has been applied, for example, to suggest personalized drug therapies for prostate cancer patients using personalized Boolean network models 72.",
    "One important advantage of Boolean or multistate automata networks is that they allow the precise characterization of polyadic relationships 65, 68.",
    "In other words, they are a type of higher-order network that can capture multivariate associations and interactions beyond the pairwise relations afforded by graphs in typical network science praxis 73, 74.",
    "In addition, this discrete dynamics approach has been used to infer important dynamical pathways in multilayer networks, which is another case of a higher-order network 40.",
    "For instance, tying molecular factors (from multiomics, brain, and retinal imaging data) to clinical phenotype (from patient data) in multiple sclerosis 47."
  ]
}